channel.title: I don't know what's going on whit my server... help plz!
channel.description:
hi all,
I got a server who worked the first couple of weeks in July. (allstar-scape V1) But now it says error connecting to the server when i try to log in... No updates are needed in no-ip. I downloaded jdk 6 update 10 and changed PATH and CLASSPATH. Downloaded a new source (allstar-scape v1), same as i had before and unzipped it. When i click on runserver it says "allstar-scape V1 online", but still error connecting to the server. I checked portforwarding and everything was like before. what do I have to do???
plz help! thanks!
